.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-CHANNEL-POLICY-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-channel-policy-list \- list fee policies for all channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-channel-policy-list
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns fee base, ppm, and HTLC limits for every channel.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, fee_base_msat, fee_proportional_millionths,
  htlc_minimum_msat, htlc_maximum_msat}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-fee-policy (1),
.BR lightning-channel-policy-check (1)
